# GenericSetupupgradestep
snippet <upgrade GenericSetupupgradestep
	<genericsetup:upgradeStep
	    title="$1"
	    description="$2"
	    source="$3"
	    destination="$4"
	    handler="$5"
	    sortkey="$6"
	    profile="$7"
	    />
	

# Interface
snippet <interface Interface
